content.p: Nottingham University Business School (NUBS) Malaysia Executive Education curates the NUBS Malaysia Masterclass Series, a platform to connect the university community, alumni and industry partners in engaging sessions with thought leaders on contemporary business ideas and challenges. Masterclasses are complimentary and are open to alumni and invited guests. To sign up for a Masterclass, please visit the relevant link below. For more information, please contact us. telephone: +6 (03) 8924 8000 fax: +6 (03) 8924 8019
